<a href="javascript:card_browser(238)">Shores of Nen Hithoel</a><br>
The <a href="javascript:card_browser(242)">Summit of Amon Hen</a><br>
<br>
Free People (36):<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(260)">Legolas, Greenleaf</a> (start)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(193)">Sam, Son of Hamfast</a> (start)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(281)">Gandalf, Friend of the Shirefolk</a> x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(245)">Aragorn, King in Exile</a> x3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(299)">Aragorn, Ranger of the North</a><br>
